# Stray artifact dropped by `shellspec --random` (e.g. the order-independence
# check). ShellSpec writes its randomized spec list to SHELLSPEC_INFILE, which
# defaults to the relative path "file" in the project root and is not cleaned
# up. Anchored so it only ignores ./file, not any nested path. See the upstream
# bug report in docs/shellspec-infile-bug.md.
/file
